> [   30.916805]
> [   30.918261] CPU: 6 PID: 387 Comm: kworker/6:2 Tainted: G           O      4.20.0-rc3Lyude-Test+ #19
> [   30.927251] Hardware name: amlogic khadas-vim2/khadas-vim2, BIOS 2018.07-rc2-armbian 09/11/2018
